<div class="modal" id="modal"><div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content"><div class="modal-body"></div><a class="link-bttn" href="../index.html" target="">More About Northwestern Engineering</a></div></div></div><div class="modal-backdrop" id="modal-backdrop"></div><div id="page" xmlns:NUWC="NUWC" xmlns:cal="xalan://java.util.GregorianCalendar"><main class="content no-default-sliders" id="department-home"><section class="leading-media cta video"><div class="cta-content contain-835"><h2>Building the Future of Northwestern Engineering</h2>
<p>A vision for leading engineering into the next era</p></div><div class="background center"><img alt="Engineering campus" src="../../images/about/strategic-plan/strategic-plan-header.jpg"/></div></section><section class="wysiwyg contain-835" style="margin-top: 70px; "><div class="header"></div><div class="contain-835"><p>It&#8217;s an exciting new era for Northwestern Engineering. Building upon our Whole-brain Engineering philosophy, we&#8217;re strategically growing our faculty in areas of leadership, improving and expanding facilities to both accelerate research and strengthen our community, fostering new and existing research collaborations, and improving our curriculum to prepare future engineers to advance the work we pursue today.</p>
<p><a class="link-arrow" href="building-our-plan.html">See how to we built our plan</a></p></div></section><section class="lg-image contain-1440" style="margin-top: 70px; margin-bottom: 70px; "><div class="feature"><img alt="strategic plan pillars" class="hero-img desktop-only lazyload" data-src="/images/about/strategic-plan/strategic-plan-pillars.svg"/><img alt="strategic plan pillars" class="hero-img mobile-only lazyload" data-src="/images/about/strategic-plan/strategic-plan-pillars_vertical.svg"/></div></section><section class="feature-cols feature-cols-unit4 contain-1440" style="margin-bottom: 70px; "><div class="header"><h2 class="title section-top contain-835">Our Strategic Pillars</h2><p class="subhead section-top-headline">Embracing the fast-changing nature of the engineering field to usher in a period of redefinition and growth</p><div class="contain-835"><p>Our vision is structured around three strategic pillars that are key to pushing engineering into the next era.</p>
<p>&#160;</p></div></div><div class="feature-three-col contain-1120"><article class="feature-box"><div class="feature-copy" style="margin-bottom: 0;"><h3 class="alternate">Revolutionize the Methods of Engineering </h3><p class="emphasized-text">The methods of engineering are changing fast.</p>
<p>Building on our current research strengths, we&#8217;ll position ourselves at the frontier of engineering by defining future methods that all engineers will need to know.</p>
<p>We will focus our work around:&#160;</p>
<ul>
<li>Biohybrid systems&#160;</li>
<li>Concurrent Materials Design&#160;</li>
<li>Going Beyond Data: Discovery, Design, and Decision-Making</li>
</ul>
&#160;<br/><a class="link-arrow" href="revolutionize-engineering-methods.html">Explore the methods</a></div></article><article class="feature-box"><div class="feature-copy" style="margin-bottom: 0;"><h3 class="alternate">Transform Engineering Education </h3><p class="emphasized-text">Innovative, adaptable curriculum is central to our mission to educate with an eye toward future challenges.</p>
<p>By working entrepreneurial thinking into our core curriculum, weaving design thinking throughout our undergraduate experience, and teaching our new methods of engineering to our students, we'll prepare the next generation of engineers to address challenges in an ever-evolving landscape.</p>
<p>Our students will benefit from:</p>
<ul>
<li>An Innovative First-year Curriculum</li>
<li>Design Thinking that Permeates</li>
<li>Flexibility and Innovation in Degree Programs</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="link-arrow" href="transform-engineering-education.html">Explore education</a></p></div></article><article class="feature-box"><div class="feature-copy" style="margin-bottom: 0;"><h3 class="alternate">Advance the Critical Applications of Engineering </h3><p class="emphasized-text">We&#8217;re tackling the grand challenges of today and tomorrow with a distinctly Northwestern mindset.&#160;</p>
<p>Equipped with our new methods of engineering and a skill set rooted in whole-brain thinking, we&#8217;ll apply our expertise in unique ways to make the greatest possible impact via these application areas:</p>
<ul>
<li>Embodied AI</li>
<li>Climate-Resilient Communities</li>
<li>Remote Environments</li>
<li>Optimize the Human Health Span</li>
</ul>
<p><a class="link-arrow" href="advance-critical-applications-of-engineering.html">Explore our applications</a></p></div></article></div></section></main></div>
       
        
